fields.name: v_EarnedPremium
fields.expression:
IIF(ExpiryYear <> GET_DATE_PART(ReportingDate,'YYYY') AND ExpiryYear <>GET_DATE_PART(ReportingDate,'YYYY')+1, IIF(TO_INTEGER(Reinsurance_Code)=56 and WrittenPremium<0,0,WrittenPremium),
WrittenPremium + ReserveBeginningBalance - ReserveEndBalance)

object.customQuery:
SELECT PMS_Policy_Reins_Transaction.Reinsurance_Transaction_Id, 
PMS_Policy_Reins_Transaction.Policy_Key, 
PMS_Policy_Reins_Transaction.Policy_Key_Code, 
PMS_Policy_Reins_Transaction.Account_Entered_Dt,
PMS_Policy_Reins_Transaction.Major_Peril,
PMS_Policy_Reins_Transaction.Major_Peril_ID, 
PMS_Policy_Reins_Transaction.Risk_State, 
PMS_Policy_Reins_Transaction.Risk_State_ID, 
PMS_Policy_Reins_Transaction.Transaction_Code, 
PMS_Policy_Reins_Transaction.Reinsurance_Code,
PMS_Policy_Reins_Transaction.Annual_Statement_Line, 
PMS_Policy_Reins_Transaction.Stateline, 
PMS_Policy_Reins_Transaction.Inception_Dt, 
PMS_Policy_Reins_Transaction.Expiration_Dt, 
PMS_Policy_Reins_Transaction.Ceded_Premium, 
PMS_Policy_Reins_Transaction.OriginalPremiumCancelAmount,
DATEADD('day', 1, LAST_DAY(CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '2 months')) as ReportingDate
FROM
 dbo.PMS_Policy_Reins_Transaction
where (
date_part(year,Expiration_Dt) = date_part(year,DATEADD('day', 1, LAST_DAY(CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '2 months')))
OR
date_part(year,Expiration_Dt) = date_part(year,DATEADD('day', 1, LAST_DAY(CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '2 months'))) + 1
OR
Account_Entered_Dt = DATEADD('day', 1, LAST_DAY(CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '2 months'))
)
and  Reinsurance_Code not like '%97'
AND Account_Entered_Dt <= DATEADD('day', 1, LAST_DAY(CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '2 months'))

object.customQuery:
SELECT PMS_Fact_Reins_Premiums_Earned.Reinsurance_Transaction_Id, PMS_Fact_Reins_Premiums_Earned.Policy_Key, PMS_Fact_Reins_Premiums_Earned.Policy_Key_Code, PMS_Fact_Reins_Premiums_Earned.Account_Entered_Dt, PMS_Fact_Reins_Premiums_Earned.Major_Peril, PMS_Fact_Reins_Premiums_Earned.Major_Peril_ID, PMS_Fact_Reins_Premiums_Earned.Risk_State, PMS_Fact_Reins_Premiums_Earned.Risk_State_ID, PMS_Fact_Reins_Premiums_Earned.Transaction_Code, PMS_Fact_Reins_Premiums_Earned.Reinsurance_Code, PMS_Fact_Reins_Premiums_Earned.Annual_Statement_Line, PMS_Fact_Reins_Premiums_Earned.Stateline, PMS_Fact_Reins_Premiums_Earned.MTD_Earned_Premium_Amt, PMS_Fact_Reins_Premiums_Earned.YTD_Earned_Premium_Amt, PMS_Fact_Reins_Premiums_Earned.Reserve_End_Balance 
FROM
 dbo.PMS_Fact_Reins_Premiums_Earned
where Account_Entered_Dt = DATEADD('day', 1, LAST_DAY(CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '3 months'))
and  case when date_part(month,DATEADD('day', 1, LAST_DAY(CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '2 months')))=1 then 
case when  date_part(year,Expiration_Dt) =  date_part(year,DATEADD('day', 1, LAST_DAY(CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '2 months')))
then 1 
else 0
end
else 1 end=1
and Reinsurance_Code<>'97'

fields.name: ReserveEndBalance
fields.expression:
IIF(ExpiryYear <> GET_DATE_PART(ReportingDate,'YYYY') AND ExpiryYear <>GET_DATE_PART(ReportingDate,'YYYY')+1,0,

(Ceded_Premium + OriginalPremiumCancelAmount) * UPRFactor)

fields.name: up_Res_EndBalance
fields.expression:
IIF(ExpiryYear <> GET_DATE_PART(ReportingDate,'YYYY') AND ExpiryYear <>GET_DATE_PART(ReportingDate,'YYYY')+1,0,
IIF(OriginalPremiumCancelAmount < 0 , OriginalPremiumCancelAmount*UPRFactor,
(Ceded_Premium + OriginalPremiumCancelAmount) *(1- UPRFactor)))
